[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "どうも、皆さんこんにちは……！\n新進気鋭グループ『ＱＥジーンズ』のキューンです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00502",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00503",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ベップよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00504",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ということで、早速始めていきたいんだけど……\nみんな、ここはどこ……なのかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00505",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "何を言ってるの。無人島よ。\nさっきボートで送ってもらったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00506",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "スケジュールに「無人島企画予定日」と記載あり。\nキューンに、健忘の兆候……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00507",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "違うよ！　こういうのは、まるで今突然\n連れて来られたみたいに振る舞うものなの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00508",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "まったくもう……二人が先に言っちゃったけど、\n今回の企画はー！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00509",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "生き抜け！　真夏の無人島サバイバルー！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00510",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "いぇーい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00511",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "みんなには……私も含めてだけど、\nこれから３日間この無人島でサバイバルしてもらいます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00512",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "泳いで脱出するのはアリなのかしら。\n私なら向こう岸まで泳げると思うわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00513",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "もちろんなしだよ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00514",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "手始めにイカダを作っておく。\nいざとなったらそれで脱出すればいい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00515",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "随分簡単に言うね……？\n確かに、ヤド姉なら作れそうだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00516",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "じゃなくて！　二人とも脱出しようって思わない！\nルールを説明するから、ちゃんと聞いてぇ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00517",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なるほど。これが最近動画投稿サイトで話題の\nグループってわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00518",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そう！　まだ活動開始して間もないんだよ！\nすごいよね、女の子なのにこんな体当たり企画をしてて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00519",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "この後本当にイカダ作っちゃうし、脱出がダメならって\n泳いで往復して、物資を持って帰って来たりするんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00520",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "かわいらしいビジュアルに加えて、個性的な三人による\n軽妙な掛け合い……バズるのも納得でありまするな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00521",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そして、この三人はカウントダウンフェスの\n審査枠に応募したことも発表している……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00522",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "つまり、ライバルってことね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00523",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "歌とダンスの動画もアップしてるみたいだよ。\n腕前は……鬼門とヨハナのほうが上手に感じるけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00524",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "見た感じ、最近レッスンを始めたばかりのイザナと\nどっこいどっこいじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00525",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それでも、再生数は伸びているようでござる。\n本人たちの「人気」ゆえの結果でありましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00526",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "もっと色んな動画を見てみよう？\nなんで「人気」なのかを、研究しなくちゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00527",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なんにせよ、フェスに出るならこの子たちに\n勝たなきゃいけないってわけね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00528",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "大丈夫よ。歌とダンスなら、負けてないんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00529",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "配信者グループ『ＱＥジーンズ』のメンバー。\nまとめ役でありツッコミ担当の常識人枠",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "配信者グループ『ＱＥジーンズ』のメンバー。\n独特な話し方がファンの間でブームとなっている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ベップ・ジムロック",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp Zimlock",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "配信者グループ『ＱＥジーンズ』のメンバー。\nマイペースな性格でキューンたちを振り回している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]